data.description:
PREFERRED LENDER OFFERS UP TO $20,000 FREE GRANT FOR CLOSING COST AND RATE BUY DOWN!!!! Come make this 2022 Lennar home yours. 
Boasting 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a world of contemporary comforts, this residence is a masterpiece of modern living.
The heart of this home is the exquisite kitchen adorned with sleek quartz countertops, providing the perfect blend of style and functionality. Imagine preparing delicious meals and entertaining friends and family in this culinary haven.

The main floor features a beautiful and spacious primary suite, offering a retreat-like atmosphere. Pamper yourself in the walk-in shower, and revel in the convenience of a generously sized closet. With the primary suite conveniently located downstairs, privacy and ease of access are at the forefro Upstairs, discover three more bedrooms that provide ample space for family or guests. Whether you're creating a home office, a cozy guest room, or a vibrant kids' space, the possibilities are endless.

Experience the joy of outdoor living in the screened-in patio, seamlessly connected to the living room. This inviting space is perfect for enjoying your morning coffee, hosting gatherings, or simply unwinding after a long day.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this Lennar home your owna perfect blend of elegance, functionality, and comfort. Live the lifestyle you deserve in this contemporary gem! Schedule your showing today!
